snippet.title: Emily D. Baker
snippet.description:
Live | TUESDAY 9:00am PST/11:00am CST/12:00amEST  &  FRIDAY 5:00pm PST/7:00pm CST/ 8:00pm EST

Hey There Law Nerd! I am Emily D. Baker, Everyone's Favorite Legal Commentator. I am a badass lawyer who breaks down the legal side of the pop culture and news stories we are all talking about. This is legal commentary that helps you understand the law with humor, Cursey Words and our own Law Nerds Dictionary. Remember, this is commentary. I know I am cool, but I am not your lawyer. This is not legal advice...it's infotainment. There is no attorney-client relationship formed through interactions with this channel or sending super chats.

Everyone’s Favorite Legal Commentator 
Badass Lawyer | Prior LA District Attorney  
🎙Host of Top 20 News Commentary Podcast The Emily Show. I break down the legal shit behind the stories we all want to talk about. 

🎤TEDx & International Speaker. Nerd. 

📲 Text Me 📱www.TextEmily.com

Understand. Evaluate. Change
